{"results":[{"aya":"022","id":5573,"locale":"id","sura":"075","text":"Wajah-wajah (orang-orang mukmin) pada hari itu berseri-seri.","translator":"Indonesian Ministry of Religious Affairs"},{"aya":"023","id":5574,"locale":"id","sura":"075","text":"Kepada Tuhannyalah mereka melihat.","translator":"Indonesian Ministry of Religious Affairs"},{"aya":"024","id":5575,"locale":"id","sura":"075","text":"Dan wajah-wajah (orang kafir) pada hari itu muram,","translator":"Indonesian Ministry of Religious Affairs"},{"aya":"025","id":5576,"locale":"id","sura":"075","text":"mereka yakin bahwa akan ditimpakan kepadanya malapetaka yang amat dahsyat.","translator":"Indonesian Ministry of Religious Affairs"},{"aya":"026","id":5577,"locale":"id","sura":"075","text":"Sekali-kali jangan. Apabila nafas (seseorang) telah (mendesak) sampai ke kerongkongan,","translator":"Indonesian Ministry of Religious Affairs"},{"aya":"027","id":5578,"locale":"id","sura":"075","text":"dan dikatakan (kepadanya): \"Siapakah yang dapat menyembuhkan?\",","translator":"Indonesian Ministry of Religious Affairs"},{"aya":"028","id":5579,"locale":"id","sura":"075","text":"dan dia yakin bahwa sesungguhnya itulah waktu perpisahan (dengan dunia),","translator":"Indonesian Ministry of Religious Affairs"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":6,"previousPage":"/id/s075-3.json","nextPage":"/id/s075-5.json"}}